project: Press any arrow to move the blue square. Collide with the Blueberry to start. Make sure to read instructions first though!
Level 1: You, as an innocent victim of pirates, escaped from the pirate ark's jailcell on the bottom deck. You begin to trek around and have to avoid crew members in the process of doing so.

Level 2: In this level, you notice a lot of blueberries. You have heard that all crew members are allergic to them. However, most of them are rotten. You have to find the actual berry in order to proceed. Hopefully with that berry you can keep the crew at bay.

Level 3: There are a couple of drinks that the crew members left behind. The drink inside a green alcoholic bottle is a booster, and can give you energy. On the other hand, the brown bottle is filled with poison. Make sure to get the green bottle and not the brown one! After you obtain the treasure chest, you notice the plank next to it. You then jump off the ark, and escape to a nearby island. Eventually, a helicopter comes and saves you. You return home well.
You did not collect the actual blueberry.
Congrats, you made it out of the ark and stole the captain's most precious loot from the chest!
